    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>After weeks of speculation, Russia's defense minister has confirmed that there will be deep cuts in the country's once-mighty military. President Vladimir V. Putin returned from New York to meet with top advisers, and detailed proposals for the cuts will be on his desk in coming days, Russian military officials said.</p>
        <p>Article, Page 16.</p>
